title: BREAKING: Massive 6.6 magnitude quake rocks Pakistan sparking tsunami fears
text:
FEARS: The quake struck just off the Pakistan coast 
The quake struck early on Wednesday and is understood to be 10km deep, USGS reports. 
The epicentre of tremor was around 90 km (55 miles) south of Turbat, Pakistan. 
There are no reports of any casualties yet. powerful #earthquake shakes Southwestern Pakistan 8 min ago.
